Activity 9
Create a computer program that asks the user a few True/False statements to which the user will respond either True or False.

T = str(input("Oceans contain salt water"))
F = str(input("Sharks are mammals"))


if T == "True":
    print ("You answered", T, "which is the correct answer!")
else: 
    print ("You answered", T, "which is the wrong answer! The correct answer is True")
if F == "True" or F == "true":
    print ("You answered", F, "which is the wrong answer! The correct answer is False")
else: 
    print ("You answered", F, "which is the correct answer!")

